div class="zm-noti7-content-body"><div class="zm-noti7-popup-loading"><span class="noti-spinner-loading"></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="zm-noti7-frame-border bottom"></div><div class="zm-noti7-popup-footer"><a href="/notifications" class="zm-noti7-popup-footer-all zg-right">查看全部 &raquo;</a><a href="/settings/notification" class="zm-noti7-popup-footer-set" title="通知设置" ><i class="zg-icon zg-icon-settings"></i></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="zu-global-notify" id="zh-global-message" style="display:none"><div class="zg-wrap"><div class="zu-global-nitify-inner"><a class="zu-global-notify-close" href="javascript:;" title="关闭" name="close">x</a><span class="zu-global-notify-icon"></span><span class="zu-global-notify-msg"></span></div></div></div><main class="pure-g receptacle"><section class="page-content-main pure-u-1 pure-u-md-17-24"><div class="unit-inner"><div class="module roundtable-profile clearfix"><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018" class="photo visible-desktop"><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-823d5358a5ae386a0147cac32a9966d4_xl.jpg" srcset="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-823d5358a5ae386a0147cac32a9966d4_b.jpg 2x" alt="2018 诺贝尔奖巡礼" class="avatar"></a><div class="content"><div class="title"><h1><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018">2018 诺贝尔奖巡礼</a></h1><span class="status">已结束</span></div><div class="description">举世瞩目的诺贝尔奖声名远播，业已成为自然科学、经济学和文学等领域的最高奖项，2018 年评选结果将于 10 月 1 日起陆续揭晓。知乎「诺贝尔奖巡礼」系列圆桌也已迎来第四个年头。今年我们再度携手中国科普博览，邀请各学科的专家学者，老时间、老地点，和大家一起畅谈诺奖、畅游科学。</div><div class="actions"><button class="button-link share pull-left" data-id="288" data-token="nobel2018"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button><span class="visits text-muted">50282366 次浏览 </span><span class="bull">&bull;</span><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018/followers" class="followers text-muted"><span class="count" data-count="14431"> 14431</span> 人关注</a></div></div></div><div class="module"><ul class="menu-nav horizontal"><li class="active"><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018">134 <span class="nowrap">条动态</span></a></li><li ><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018/questions">81 <span class="nowrap">个问题</span></a></li><li ><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018/comments">32 <span class="nowrap">条讨论</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="feeds loose"><ul class="items" data-paging="{&quot;next&quot;: &quot;/r/roundtables/nobel2018/activities?offset=21&quot;}" data-navigable><li class="item" data-type="Question"><link itemprop="url" href="/question/36290798"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="6723431"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="36290798"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="link" target="_blank" href="/question/36290798">有哪些人为诺奖得主的理论形成贡献了力量，却没能分享诺奖？</a></h2></div><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="6723431"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">1 条评论</span></button></li><li class="bull">&bull;</li><li><a href="/question/36290798">13 个回答</a></li></ul></div></li><li class="item" data-type="Answer"><a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-121628885"></a><link itemprop="url" href="/question/297127181/answer/503575698"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="28305107"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="297127181"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="121628885"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="503575698"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/297127181/answer/503575698">有哪些诺贝尔奖得主拥有硬核的人生？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>298</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">298</span><span class="