ms"><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/li-miao-7" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$li-miao-7'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/37411037359278e65eba66c9a74a411d_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="李淼"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018/li-miao-7/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/li-miao-7" data-hovercard='p$t$li-miao-7'>李淼</a><span class="icon icon-badge-identity icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$已认证的个人"></span><div class="bio">理论物理以及诗歌</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/fuwocheng" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$fuwocheng'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c096f565bad088a2b709d460f066e1dc_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="傅渥成"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018/fuwocheng/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/fuwocheng" data-hovercard='p$t$fuwocheng'>傅渥成</a><span class="icon icon-badge-id-an icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$优秀回答者 · 已认证的个人"></span><div class="bio">东京大学 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 博士后</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/sijichun" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$sijichun'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8906a56d80b98224eb1d544c9dc69c74_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="慧航"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018/sijichun/answers" class="answers text-muted">4 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/sijichun" data-hovercard='p$t$sijichun'>慧航</a><span class="icon icon-badge-id-an icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$优秀回答者 · 已认证的个人"></span><div class="bio">上海对外经贸大学 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 讲师</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/divinites" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$divinites'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2136abf2d4081f2ee9493cd1f10109e3_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="司马懿"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018/divinites/answers" class="answers text-muted">3 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/divinites" data-hovercard='p$t$divinites'>司马懿</a><span class="icon icon-badge-id-an icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$优秀回答者 · 已认证的个人"></span><div class="bio">爱丁堡大学 (University of Edinburgh) <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 助理教授</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/jiehou1993" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$jiehou1993'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/1eb9b8c7e7ddc53f26db62a3ecd99dd7_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="小侯飞氘"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018/jiehou1993/answers" class="answers text-muted">4 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/jiehou1993" data-hovercard='p$t$jiehou1993'>小侯飞氘</a><span class="icon icon-badge-identity icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$已认证的个人"></span><div class="bio">麦吉尔大学 (McGill University) <span class="bull">&bull;</span> Graduate Research Trainee</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/meng-xiao-meng-29-98" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$meng-xiao-meng-29-98'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ace43959eb3062b2bec741a7dcf1e392_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="孟凡康"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018/meng-xiao-meng-29-98/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/meng-xiao-meng-29-98" data-hovercard='p$t$meng-xiao-meng-29-98'>孟凡康</a><span class="icon icon-badge-identity icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$已认证的个人"></span><div class="bio">iGEM <span class="bull">&bull;</span> NKU_China Team Leader（2016）/ UCAS Advisor（2017）</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/dong-yu-long-37" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$dong-yu-long-37'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5610df4c0db